175 A.3d 156 JAMES A. YURCHAK, APPELLANT-PETITIONER, v. NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, RESPONDENT-RESPONDENT.

C-262 September Term 2017

080038 October 26, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

*301A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004140-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
